                  <summary/>
            
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="20r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4520Prayer">Prayer of Our Lady Mary to Jesus Christ, for 21 miyāzyā</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎት፡ ዘእግዝ<supplied reason="omitted">እ</supplied>ትነ፡ 
                        ማርያም፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ እሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘጸውዐቶ፡ አመ፡ ፭፡ ዓመት፡ ወ፭አውራኅ፡ አመ፡ 
                           <sic>፳ወ፩ለምያዝያ።</sic>
                         ማርያም፡ ቅድስት፡ 
                        ድንግል፡ ከሠተት፡ አፉሃ፡ 
                           <sic>ቅዱስ፡</sic>
                         ዘምሉእ፡ ብርሃን፡ ወኵሎሙ፡ አሕዛብ፡ ይፈርሁ፡ እመለኮተ፡ ወልዳ፨ ወተናገረት፡ በፍቅረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወበዐቢይ፡ 
                        ክብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፨ በገንስጦስ፨ በድንስጥስ፨ ጰሆራይስ፨ ፑፒሮስ፨ አርስድስጦስ፨ ረአይስጢስ፨ ጰአኩጰአው፨ 
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        አርሜስ፡ ገጸ፡ አንበሳ፡ አግርሜጥር፨ ገጸ፡ ሰብእ፨ በርቲና፨ ላህም፨ አርጣን፨ ገጸ፡ ንስር፨ ለቀዳማዊ፡ ገጸ፡ አንበሳ፡ አምሳለ፡ ፈጣሪሁ፡ 
                           <sic>ዝወእቱ፡</sic>
                         አብ፡ 
                        
                           <sic>ወከልእ፡</sic>
                         ገጽ፡ ከመ፡ ሰብእ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ነስአ፡ ፍጹመ፡ ሱባኤ፨ ለሣልስ፡ ገጹ፡ ከመ፡ ንስር፡ አምሳለ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ አስተርአየ፡ በርእየተ፨ ርግብ፡ 
                        በስጋ፨ ወለራብዕ፨ ገጹ፡ ከመ፡ ላህም፨ አምሳለ፨ ቅድስት፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፨ አከኤል፨ ፈኑኤል፨ ገኑኤል፨ ጸትኤል፨ አፍድኤል፨ ዝራኤል፨ ኤል፨ ኤል፨ ተዳኤል፨ 
                        <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ፔለልኤል፨ ታልደኤል፨ ፓስዱኤል፨ ኤል፨ ልኤል፨
                     </explicit>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="20r" to="29r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4299Prayer">Prayer of Our Lady Mary to Jesus Christ at the sepulchre</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ፀሎት፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ንጽሕት፡ ወላዲተ፡ 
                        ሕይወት፡ 
                           <sic>እንቀጸ፡</sic>
                         ብርሃን፡ ዓዘቅተ፡ ክብር፡ መስተምሕርት፡ ለኵሉ፡ ዓለም፨ ጸሎታ፡ ወስእለታ፡ 
                           <sic>ያሀሉ፨</sic>
                         
                        ምስሌነ፡ ለዓለም፨ አሜን፨ ወእምዝ፡ ሰፍሐት፡ እደዊሃ፡ ወአንቃዕደወት፡ 
                           <sic>ለዕለ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ወስተ፡</sic>
                         ሰማይ፨ 
                        ወከልሐት፡ ወጸርኃት፡ ኀበ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልድ፡ እንዘ፡ ትብል፨ ነዓ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ወልታ፡ ጽድቅ፡ 
                           <sic>ዘእምያማን፡</sic>
                         ወዘእምፀጋም፨ ነዓ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ 
                        
                           <sic>ቀደማወ፡</sic>
                         በኵርየ፡ ፍቁርየ፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ምርሖ፡ ፍኖተ፡ መድኃኒት፡ ወስረይ፡ ሎቱ፡ 
                           <sic>ኵሉ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ኃጢአቱ፡</sic>
                         በዳግም፡ 
                           <sic>ምጸአትከ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>በኀለይ፡</sic>
                         ዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፨ አዮ፡ አዮ። ዳኬ። ዳኬ። = ። 
                           <sic>ለዓለም፤</sic>
                         ዓለም፨ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="29r" to="44v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4343Prayer">Prayers of Our Lady Mary to the Christ Child</title> 
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> 
                        
                           <sic>ጸሎቱ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ዘእግዚእትነ።</sic>
                         ቅድስት፡ 
                           <sic>ደንግል፡</sic>
                         ማርያም፡ ንጽሕት፡ ጸሎታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን፨ =፨ ወኮነ፡ 
                        በኃምስ፡ 
                           <sic>ዓምት፡</sic>
                         በአሚሩ፡ እምኃምስ፡ ወርኅ። ቆመት፡ ማርያም፨ ድንግል፡ ቅድስት፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ከመ፡ 
                           <sic>ይኵኑ፨</sic>
                         ባቲ፡ መድኃኒት፡ 
                           <sic>ወሐሴተ፡</sic>
                         ለገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ እምኀበ፡ ኀይለ፡ አብ፨ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ 
                        ቅዱስ፨ ይእዜኒ፡ ወዘልፈኒ፨ ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፨
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                     at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="44v" to="49r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3138Negeranni">Nǝgǝranni sǝmaka</title>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="49r" to="54v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4521Prayer">Prayer of Our Lady Mary to Jesus Christ before the labour</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎቱ፡ 
                           <sic>ዘእግዚእትነ፡</sic>
                         
                        ማርያም፨ 
                           <sic>ዘጸለያት፡</sic>
                         ወትቤ። በርታፍከዮስ፡ ተኀዝልፍዮስ፡ ዓምድወዮስ። ዘቆሮልየስ፨ እንበኮብያኤል፨ ታኤል፨ አልሞድቃኤል፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ዬ፨ ዬ፡ ዬዬ፨ ቆኆኆቴከ፨ ዬዬዬ፨ ታ፨ ታቱታ፨ ቴቱ፨ ቱቱቱታ፨ በዝንቱ፡ ቃል፡ ተዘከር፡ ሥጋከ፡ 
                           <sic>ወደምከ፡</sic>
                         ፫አስማት፡ ማእስሮሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፨ ከመ፡ 
                        መርበብተ፡ ዓሣ፡ ባሕር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus from="55r" to="59r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4522Magic">Magical prayer against the demons</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> አወግዘከ፡ ሰይጣን፡ በ፼አእላፍ፡ ወትእልፊተ፡ አእላፋት፡ 
                        መላእክት። በሚካኤል፨ ወበገብርኤል፨ በሱራፌል፨ ወበኪሩቤል፨ በሩፋኤል፨ ወበኡራኤል፨ ወበአባ፡ አጋቶን፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ተማህፀንኩ፡ በእግዚአ፡ ሰማያት፡ ወምድር፡ አነ፡ ገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ አስማተ፡ እግዚእነ፨ ብያቴር፨ ምናቴር፨ ድማሄል፨ አሙናኤል፨ ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለእግዚአ፡ 
                        ብርሃናት፡ ብርሃነ፡ ማኅቶት፡ ዘኢይጠፍእ፡ ብርሃን፡ ዘኢይጸልም፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ ቃለ፡ ፍዳ፨ በዝንቱ፡ ስምከ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ አነ፡ ገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                        at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <locus from="59r" to="63r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4523Prayer">Prayer of the penance over the water</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ጸሎተ፡ ንስሓ። ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ወይቤሎ፡ 
                        ንሳእ፡ ወሀብኩከ፡ ዘንተ፡ መራኁተ፡ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ከመ፡ ትእስር፡ ወትፍታሕ፡ ይቤሎ፡ እግዚኣብሔር፡ አብ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልድ፨ ጸጋ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ ኤልሳኤልኮስ፨ 
                        ጰንታካ<add place="inline">
                           <supplied reason="omitted">ራ</supplied>
                        </add>ጢሮስ፨ አጌማሙስ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> 
                        ወይኩን፡ ፍቱሐ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ማይ፡ እማእሰሩ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ፈኑ፡ ላዕሌየ፡ ወላዕለ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ማይ፡ መንፈስከ፡ ቅዱሰ፨ ከመ፡ ዐቃቤ፡ ወመራኄ፨ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ወበኵለሄ፡ አሜን፡ አሜን፨ በቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን። ለይኩን፡ ዘንተ፡ ፍትሐተ፡ ፫ጊዜ፡ 
                        በል፡ ዲበ፡ ዘይት፡ ፩ጊዜ፡ ዲበ፡ ማኅቶት፡ ፩ጊዜ፡ ዲበ፡ ማይ፨
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="63r" to="65r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4524Prayer">Untitled prayer containing magical names</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> አስማተ፡ ኀይል፨ ኢያሄድ፨ አፍናኤል፨ አስናኤል፨ አቅናኤል፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ገጠመኤኬል፨ ምክሌሳውናመላላካኤል። እምሰብዐቱ፡ መሳክወ፡ ሰማያት፡ ይምጻእ፡ ምሕረት፡ በአዳኤል። በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ላዕለ፡ ገብርከ፡ ሕዝበ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ለዓለ<supplied reason="omitted">ም</supplied>፡ 
                        ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11460HezbaK">Ḥǝzba Krǝstos</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                        at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <locus from="65r" to="76v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4525Prayer">Magical prayer with the names that Jesus Christ gave to the apostles durin his Ascension</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ ስሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መላኬ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወሥጋ። ሰላትያል። ኤላዊ። ኤሌዌ፡ ዝሕቅያሔሕ። በራባ፡ ኤላዊ፡ ኤላዌ፡ አላላዊ። ብርኤል፡ 
                        ከ<add place="inline">
                           <supplied reason="omitted">ነ</supplied>
                        </add>ደናዊ፨ 
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወይስግድ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወይጠመቅ፡ በማየ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ጸሎት፡ ወኢይትናገር፡ ምንተኒ፡ እስከ፡ ይነሥእ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ዕቀብ፡ ወተሐዩ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ አሜን፨ ወአሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10">
                     <locus from="77r" to="81v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4526Waanani">Untitled prayer</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወአነኒ፡ 
                           <sic>አምኀፅን፡</sic>
                         ነፍስየ፡ ወስጋየ፡ በዕፀ፡ መስቀልከ፡ ክቡር፡ በዘቦቱ፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ 
                           <sic>ግዕዛነ፡</sic>
                         ለኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ 
                        ወበአስማቲከ፡ ሠናያት፡ ዘትምሕር፡ ቦሙ፡ አግብርቲከ፡ ወከማሁ፡ መሐረኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ። ስምዖን። በዝ፡ ዓለም፡ ወበዘይመጽእ፡ ዓለም። ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ 
                           <sic>ወከዕበ፡</sic>
                         
                        አመኀፅን፡ ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ዘላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘፈጠረ፡ 
                           <sic>ኵሉ፡</sic>
                         በጥበቡ፨ አመኀጽን፡ ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ኀቤሁ፨ ወዓዲ፡ አመሐጽን፡ 
                        ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ኀቤሁ፡ ወኀበ፡ መንበሩ፡ ወኀበ፡ ወልዱ፡ ዘእምአብ፡ ተወልደ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ተፈጥረ፡ ኵሉ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ትዕቀበኒ፡ ወትትማኅፀነኒ፡ ከመ፡ ብንተ፡ ዐይን፡ ለገብርከ። ስምዖን። ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ አድኅነኒ፡ እምፀዓዕ፡ ወመብረቅ፡ ወሕማመ፡ ከብድ፡ ለገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formulas 
                        at the beginning and the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11">
                     <locus from="81v" to="85v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4527Magic">Magical names against the deeds of the Antichrist</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> አስማት፡ በዘይጸራዕ፡ ግብሩ፡ ለሐሳዌ፡ መሲሕ፡ ወበዘይትአኰት፡ 
                        ግብሩ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ወትብል፡ ዘንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ክሥት፡ ዘንተ፡ ዘንጸርኅ፡ ኀቤከ፡ በከመ፡ ቀጥቀጥከ፡ መናስግተ፡ ኀጺን፡ በርደትከ፡ ውስተ፡ ሲኦል፨ ወነሠትከ፡ አረፋቲሃ፡ 
                        ለሲኦል፨ ከመ፡ ታድኅን፡ ልሕኵተከ፡ ግብረ፡ እደዊከ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        አብዝድ፨ ከዋዲ፨ ኀጢከሊዮን፨ ስእፋስ፨ ድድእወራይስት፡ በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ አነ፡ ገብርከ፡ ስምዖን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                        <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                           at the end of the text.</note>
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12">
                     <locus from="86r" to="87r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4528Magic">Magical prayer against the deeds of the Antichrist</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሐፍነ፡ በዘ፡ ንዜከር፡ አስማተ፡ 
                           <sic>ቅድስት፡</sic>
                         በዘይጸራዕ፡ ግብሩ፡ ለሐሳዌ፡ መሲሕ፡ ወበዘይጸንዕ፡ ሃይማኖተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በእግዚእነ፡ በኑፋኤል፨ 
                        ስምከ፨ አድኅነኒ፡ እምኀይለ፡ ጸላኢ፨ በአውባኤል፨ ስምከ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ አድኅነኒ፡ እምሐፅ፡ ኅቡእ፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ቱታላኤል፨ በርስላፋኤዴንን፨ ኢዮቢ፨ አነ፡ ውእቱ፡ ሰይፈ፡ እሳት፡ ወልደ፡ ጋዴን፨ ወበዝንቱ፡ አስማት፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ከመ፡ ትምሐረኒ፡ ለገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ሊትናዊት፨ 
                        ቂትናዊት፨ ሙራናሎዊ፨ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> እግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሊተ፡ 
                        ርድአኒ፡ ለገብርከ፨ ስምዖን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formulas 
                        at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i13">
                     <locus from="88v" to="91r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4529Godorek">Untitled magical prayer</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጎዶሬከንድቄሌሌንዮላፌንጡጡሬንቃሮዴኔዎንድማሄሬን፡ ዘንተ፡ ኅቡአ፡ አስማተ፡ ትደግም፡ በልሑሳሥ፡ ወይከውነከ፡ ጸጋ፡ ወሞገሠ፨ ወበደኀሪት፡ ዕለት፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ነፍስከ፨ 
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ያሮክ፨ ያሮክ፨ ያሮቶስ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ወአ<add place="inline">
                           <supplied reason="omitted">ማ</supplied>
                        </add>ኅፀንኩ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ወሥጋየ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይቅረበኒ፡ ነኪር፡ 
                        ለገብርከ፨ 
                           <sic>ስምዐን፡</sic>
                         ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ለይኩን፨ ለይኩን፨
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                        at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i14">
                     <locus from="91r" to="92r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4530Magic">Magical names of God</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ያሮስ፡ ለያ፡ ማሙታ፡ ኢላክ፨ አስያር፨ ላሜምዶአልከ፡ 
                        ለሜኤድ፡ አልማድ፡ ኤሎሄ፨ ኤልማስ፨ ለማ፨ ሰበቀተኒ፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ተማኅፀንኩ፡ 
                           <sic>በስመከ፡</sic>
                         ያኤል፡ ግበር፡ ሊተ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘእፈቅድ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ፨ 
                           <sic>ስመዖን፡</sic>
                         ከመ፡ 
                        እርከብ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘፈቀድኩ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner of the book <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11459Semon">Sǝmʿon</persName> is mentioned in the supplication formula 
                        at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i15">
                     <locus from="92r" to="95r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4531Magic">Magical names of Jesus Christ</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> አስማተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሴዴር፨ ላዊ፨ ላደጋዊ፨ 
                        ቄዶላዳላዊ፨ ቄዶላላዊ፨ ቄዶላላኤል፨ ቄዶሩ፨
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወትነሥእ፡ ፯ቃላተ፡ ወትነሥእ፡ ጽንሓሐ፡ ወታነብብ፡ ፯ጊዜ፨ ወበበ፯ቃላት፡ ወትረክብ፡ ትእምርቶ፡ ወትጠመቅ፡ ወትከውን፡ ከመ፡ ሕፃን፡ ዘኢለከፎ፡ ርስሐተ፡ ኀጢአት፨
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i16">
                     <locus from="95r" to="101r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4532Prayer">Magical prayer revealed by Jesus Christ to obtain the eternal salvation</title>
                     <note/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> 
                        
                           <sic>ነገር፡</sic>
                         
                        ንነግረክሙ፡ ዘነገረነ፡ መድኀኒነ፡ በዘንድኅን፡ በደኃሪት፡ ዕለት፡ ወበይእቲ፡ ሰዐት፡ አሜሃ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ወኃጥኣን፡ ኵሎሙ፡ በበአሐዱ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ወአሜሃ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ 
                           <sic>ፀሓየ፡</sic>
                         
                        
                           <sic>ወወርኀ፡</sic>
                         ወከዋክብትኒ፡ ይወድቁ፡ እምሰማይ፡ ምስለ፡ 
                        ብርሃኖሙ፡ ወትመጽእ፡ ጽዮን፡ ሐዳስ፡ መርዓት፡ ወይወርድ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እጓለ፡ እመ፡ ሕያው፡ ወይለብስ፡ አልባሰ፡ ከርቦኖጌ፨ ዘስሙ፡ ገራዝዮን፨ 
                           <sic>ወይቤሉ፡</sic>
                         
